KINGFISHER

CLIENT REFERRAL PROGRAM TEMPLATE

The Kingfisher Template is the best option for your client referral program. This referral program template empowers your existing clients with the advocacy tools they need to successfully share your services, monitor referral activity, and get paid. It is ideal for your SaaS referral programs, allows multiple payment options (PayPal, prepaid Visa gift cards, and coupons), and it's available in 20 languages.
This client referral program template is built with Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is easily customizable, fully responsive, and supports all current browsers and devices.
TRY IT NOW
LIVE PREVIEW
This client referral program template has no traditional registration and login forms. Registration is provided via a seamless access form where your clients enter their email addresses. You can also skip this step by using our one-click access link tool or add your custom fields to this access form to collect additional information from your clients.

The advocate stats section delivers deep insight into their referral program account, allowing advocates to review their performance and focus on the client advocacy tools that work. The advocate can quickly check the total referrals and rewards, the list of referrals, bonuses, and their status.

ADVOCATE INSIGHTS

ADVOCATE PAYMENT METHODS

Multiple advocate payment methods are available on this client referral program template, and you can activate different advocate payment methods to allow them to choose their preferred payment method. Vouchers, prepaid Amazon gift cards, and PayPal cash are the more attractive advocates' payment method options when building a client referral program.
